  "remarks": "\nMohammed Bouyeri was a member of the (now disbanded) Islamist terrorist Hofstad Group. Bouyeri murdered the film director Theo van Gogh in the Netherlands 2004. In 2005 he was found guilty of murder and of membership of a terrorist organisation.",
